Hash Handler
  get hash value
  - if hash
    - find navPage element with hash as ID
      - if found
        changeView(hash, navPage)
      - not found
        goToDefaultPage()
  - no hash
    goToDefaultPage()
      
goToDefaultPage() {
    get default hash
    - if given
        change hash to default hash
    - not given
        find 1st navPage element
        - if found 
        get the navPage element's ID
        - if exists
            change hash to the navPage element's ID
        - not exists
            return error.
        - not found
        return error.
}

changeView(hash, navPage) {

  hideAllNavPages()
  
  activateNavPage(navPage);
  activateNavLink(hash);
  
  getNavPageContentIfExists(hash);

  window.scrollTo(0, 0);
}
